---
title: StudioLedger — Milestone Lifecycle State Machine
---
stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Draft
  Draft --> Proposed: propose terms
  Proposed --> Funded: fund escrow (EscrowCreate)

  Funded --> Submitted: creator submits work
  Funded --> Disputed: either party disputes

  Submitted --> Approved: client approves
  Submitted --> Funded: request changes (deliverables cleared)
  Submitted --> Disputed: either party disputes

  Approved --> Released: release escrow (EscrowFinish)
  Approved --> Disputed: either party disputes

  Released --> MCC_Minted: auto-mint T1 + T4

  Disputed --> Resolved: panel vote / admin ruling
  Resolved --> Released: creator wins → release
  Resolved --> Refunded: client wins → refund

  MCC_Minted --> [*]
  Refunded --> [*]

  note right of Funded
    0.98% fee deducted on release
    via creator wallet seed decryption
  end note

  note right of MCC_Minted
    T1 = Work Credential (creator)
    T4 = Client Completion (marketplace)
    Metadata stored on IPFS via Pinata
  end note

  note left of Disputed
    3-member arbitration panel
    Votes: creator / marketplace / split
    Escalation to boss admin on deadlock
  end note
